---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Hearth · A quiet workspace"
  description="Projects, memos, schedule — all in one place. A local workspace your AI agent can drive."
  locale="en"
  path="/"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section data-home class="bg-ink text-paper">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24 md:px-12 md:py-40">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-5 mb-12 md:gap-6 md:mb-16">
        <img src="/icon-512.png" alt="Hearth" class="w-[clamp(96px,14vw,168px)] h-auto rounded-[22%] shadow-2xl" />
        <p class="text-paper/60 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">Hearth · macOS</p>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-[clamp(3.5rem,12vw,9rem)] font-extralight leading-[0.95] tracking-[-0.04em]">
        A quiet<br/>workspace.
      </h1>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-16 md:mt-16">
        <p class="text-xl text-paper md:text-2xl leading-snug">
          Projects, memos, schedule — all in one place.<br/>
          A local workspace your AI agent can drive.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-paper/70 leading-relaxed md:text-lg">
          Your data lives only on your Mac. Tell Claude Code what you want; hearth-cli writes it down; the open Hearth window refreshes instantly. Use it like an extension of your hand.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:gap-4 md:mt-16">
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/hearth/id0000000000" class="inline-block rounded-xl bg-paper px-6 py-3.5 text-ink font-medium hover:bg-bone transition-colors">Get it on the Mac App Store</a>
        <a href="/en/install/cli" class="inline-block rounded-xl border border-paper/30 px-6 py-3.5 text-paper font-medium hover:border-paper transition-colors">Install CLI</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES (3 hook rows) -->
  <section data-home class="bg-paper">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-24 md:px-12 md:py-32">
      <p class="text-ink/70 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">Three things, one place</p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem)] font-light leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.025em]">
        One screen where work stays.
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-20 grid gap-16 md:gap-20">
        <article class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[180px_1fr] md:gap-12 border-t border-ink/10 pt-12">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ink/70 tracking-wider uppercase md:pt-1">01 · Projects</p>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium leading-tight md:text-3xl tracking-tight">It starts with a single line.</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-ink/70 leading-relaxed md:text-lg">The moment you give it a name, scattered work moves under it. Memos, schedule, attachments — all branches of one project.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[180px_1fr] md:gap-12 border-t border-ink/10 pt-12">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ink/70 tracking-wider uppercase md:pt-1">02 · Memos</p>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium leading-tight md:text-3xl tracking-tight">A pen in your hand in 0.3 seconds.</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-ink/70 leading-relaxed md:text-lg"><code class="bg-ink/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Cmd+Shift+M</code>. Catch passing thoughts on the spot. Short notes, long writing — same place.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[180px_1fr] md:gap-12 border-t border-ink/10 pt-12">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ink/70 tracking-wider uppercase md:pt-1">03 · Schedule</p>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium leading-tight md:text-3xl tracking-tight">See just today, or pull tomorrow into view.</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-ink/70 leading-relaxed md:text-lg">Hold time's weight in one screen. Don't let alerts wash it away — handle it yourself.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIFFERENTIATOR -->
  <section data-home class="bg-ink text-paper">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-24 md:px-12 md:py-32">
      <p class="text-paper/50 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">Agent-native, by design</p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem)] font-light leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.025em]">
        Claude Code drives it directly.
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-16 md:mt-16">
        <p class="text-lg text-paper md:text-xl leading-snug">
          Say what you want; <code class="bg-paper/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">hearth-cli</code> writes it down,<br/>
          and the open Hearth refreshes immediately.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-paper/70 leading-relaxed md:text-lg">
          'Leave a memo for tomorrow's agenda' — one natural sentence and your workspace moves. No context switch — your agent uses your tools the way you do.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 aspect-video w-full rounded-xl bg-paper/5 border border-paper/10">
        <!-- App Preview video slot (Day 13 embed) -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOCAL-FIRST -->
  <section data-home class="bg-paper">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-24 md:px-12 md:py-32 text-center">
      <p class="text-ink/70 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">Local-first, no server</p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem)] font-light leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.025em]">
        No server.<br/>You know the coordinates.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-8 text-base text-ink/70 leading-relaxed md:text-lg">
        All your data lives in a single SQLite file.<br class="hidden md:inline"/>
        Time Machine backs it up; the CLI reads and writes it.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-lg bg-ink/5 px-4 py-3 font-mono text-sm text-ink/80">
        ~/Library/Application Support/com.codewithgenie.hearth/data.db
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section data-home class="bg-ink text-paper">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-20 md:px-12 md:py-28 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.75rem)] font-light leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em]">
        Start your workspace now.
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 md:flex-row md:gap-4">
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/hearth/id0000000000" class="inline-block rounded-xl bg-paper px-6 py-3.5 text-ink font-medium hover:bg-bone transition-colors">Get it on the Mac App Store</a>
        <a href="/en/install/cli" class="inline-block rounded-xl border border-paper/30 px-6 py-3.5 text-paper font-medium hover:border-paper transition-colors">Install CLI</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
